Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移民曆325年9月7日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在主張大叛亂的\N反政府組織據點中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得謝爾蓋·王中尉的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們就是\N渴望這古風琴之力的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名解放汝之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既是編織者又是守護者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓我見識妳的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籍貴與受到保護前的經歷不明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測是被以綁架\N或人口買賣等手段帶到組織裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既是編織者又是守護者啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然的惡作劇？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惘的劍打不倒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷惘呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將彼此重疊的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖進記憶深處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨而下的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我訴說著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守護」的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾度仰望 無限寬闊的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了 那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱切地 強烈地 勇猛地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在沒有光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能感覺到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你能發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第21話 白色公主，覺醒之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，大家來吃飯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白已經很適應了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我跟妳混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說愛莉卡啊，我們今後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來，有話要跟妳們講
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，在黑谷之村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟應該是女王的乙HiME在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果黑谷的人殺過來\N原本是打算親自擊退他們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓在風華宮的\N阿爾泰小鬼知道一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太亂來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟要攻打卡迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會原諒背叛我們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要讓他們知道這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要將\N阿格斯十四世一族的黨羽趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我昨晚問題的答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我們借妳力量嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以血洗血，以牙還牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們黑谷的鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被打了就想辦法報復
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本沒辦法解決事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆是這樣跟我講的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那傢伙說了一樣的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不想解決事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報復是為了保護我們自身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑谷是受詛咒的民族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不容許存在的民族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個評語長久以來守護著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種作法絕對是錯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好沒有發現這裡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備掃蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃蕩是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫德的難民嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，頭領，請救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的鐵則不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近村子的人就該死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的位置已經被卡迪亞知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰能斷定這不是陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白妳也來拜託她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些人把葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連女王也捨棄他們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，或許是妳先被他們捨棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子輪不到我們動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻生物…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被大夥丟下會沒命喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是一邊看著城堡一邊想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那高高在上的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王根本就看不到我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的，我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王\N一定會成為一個優秀的王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，靠妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天的青玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作，妳振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳振作點啊，咪咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志願軍是以上5位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是照這情勢來看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後應該會繼續增加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些女孩可信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，無須擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一戴上GEM\N我們的乙HiME…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神是無法背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，該不會是\N用了在奴獸上用的GEM的機關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼事不宜遲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請女武神部隊做點事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情報指出真白的所在地了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然情報來源的卡迪亞\N本身很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愛莉卡好像也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過情況改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要愛莉卡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了這一步，她有點礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還需要真白的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能去抓她來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，關於歌的部份…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是她沒醒來的話怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我謝爾蓋·王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將之完美地達成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿爾泰的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從出生就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，妳也扮演好自己的角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一位乙HiME的身份\N好好守護大公殿下，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王牌漸漸湊齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只要在\N得到最後一把鑰匙的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看要怎麼運用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為科學的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由它所指引出的是毀滅之路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是閃耀的未來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這不是妳該決定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不認為是這樣嗎？真祖小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會讓我想起愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾經說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就算是朋友\N乙HiME還是要互相爭鬥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自己，就不會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會讓它發生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我私底下不斷懷疑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是所有乙HiME的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，不論人還是國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都避免不了爭執的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓這樣的世界遠離破滅之路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖她才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，我當然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為此把很多學生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當成犧牲品送出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我現在能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻只有這樣祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否讓我一同祈禱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算祈禱也於事無補喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白，可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備前去進行\N追捕真白公主與愛莉卡的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能順利追捕到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會向殿下請求\N關於學園長的處置事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會不抱期望等著的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖，乖，乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請忘了今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨妳高興要怎樣都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的倒是有點好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲捲捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲捲捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲捲…捲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲…捲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近老是作怪夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再做這種事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以在這裡就放棄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～誰～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，詩帆，妳捲捲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是千繪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事想拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子\N是從卡迪亞傳出來的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王在黑谷？這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，來源相當可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的議會呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還要花上一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我認為可以信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到卡迪亞去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要搭便車？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下，能否借用車輛或船隻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我們安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝您撥冗前來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎您，安南王古恩陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒有空間收容外人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是給傷患治療\N就已經是破天荒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人已經動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是現在被丟在沙漠的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼執著？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人瞧不起妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認同妳是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還殺了妳的侍女耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是無法丟下他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳背負得了這麼多條命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要救他們，就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會…死嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別死，我不會讓妳死！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…報應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該被責怪的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害葵…和妳都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都…笑臉常開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可以…一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…又…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是溫德布倫的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白·布蘭·杜·溫德布倫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是好王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以害大家受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在也有人在恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們願意給我機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想當王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改正過去的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著人民，聽取人民的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當一個能引導大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的王…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會賭上這條命守護你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也把你們的命交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時讓這些人安頓在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以溫德布倫女王的身份\N所提出的請求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我奪回國家的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將妳所需要的\N加爾德羅貝技術交給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳辦得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我會辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛我們的人會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑谷的頭領啊，我向妳發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就相信妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫德布倫女王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白·布蘭·杜·溫德布倫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能更早…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼你們做出那種事的不是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，這是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要現在一下下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳胸前借我一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奪回國家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家都能歡笑之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的公主說不定是妳耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是當不了女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想成為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還有很多事不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是希望能夠守護重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼以我的乙HiME的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我妳的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我…不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了溫德布倫的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳問過我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於乙HiME力量的是非
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這妳自己決定就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由妳…和妳的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們去不了星星的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要實踐復仇誓言！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們出門了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校的判斷分毫不差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出情報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並打算與他們槓上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿格斯皇帝的如意算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用陪他們攪和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慎重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算攪和了也沒差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，開始作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:22:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.95,0:23:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你披著披風時頭上的角怎麼辦啊\N（破滅之歌）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模模看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好軟喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還可以伸縮喔，咻咻咻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸長～縮短～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿唷嘿唷嘿唷，哇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉德，你的病已經入侵腦部了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
